---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Child Safety Policy - Loud Space',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-10">Child Safety Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-lg mb-6">
      Loud Space is committed to providing a safe, respectful, and supportive environment for all users. We strictly
      prohibit any content, behavior, or activity that involves, promotes, or suggests child sexual abuse or
      exploitation (CSAE) in any form.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">üö´ Prohibited Content and Behavior</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">The following are strictly not allowed on Loud Space:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>Content that depicts or describes sexual exploitation or abuse of minors.</li>
      <li>Any text, imagery, audio, video, or emoji that suggests, normalizes, or glorifies CSAE.</li>
      <li>
        Attempts to solicit, share, or distribute material involving CSAE, including through links or external sources.
      </li>
      <li>Sharing or requesting personally identifiable information (PII) from minors.</li>
      <li>Attempts to contact minors for inappropriate purposes.</li>
      <li>Grooming behavior in any form, including subtle manipulation or emotional coercion.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">üîç Detection & Moderation</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>All posts are subject to automated and human moderation to detect and remove CSAE-related content.</li>
      <li>We use a combination of AI systems and manual review to flag and act on suspicious or harmful behavior.</li>
      <li>Reports by users are taken seriously and reviewed immediately.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">‚öñÔ∏è Enforcement</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>Any user found violating these standards will face immediate account suspension or termination.</li>
      <li>
        When necessary, we will report violations to relevant legal authorities in accordance with applicable laws.
      </li>
      <li>We cooperate fully with child protection organizations and law enforcement.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">üõ°Ô∏è Our Commitment to Safety</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
      <li>We do not allow anonymous access to minors.</li>
      <li>Age verification and identity checks may be requested when suspicious behavior is detected.</li>
      <li>
        We actively work to maintain a zero-tolerance policy on CSAE and partner with external agencies to stay
        up-to-date on best practices.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">üì¢ Reporting CSAE Content</h2>
    <p class="text-lg">
      If you encounter any content or behavior that you believe violates these standards, please report it immediately
      using the in-app reporting feature or contact us at <a
        href="mailto:hurdalab@gmail.com"
        class="text-accent hover:underline">hurdalab@gmail.com</a
      >. Your reports are confidential and reviewed with priority.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>

